EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
1. DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ FROM
   7.5 METER S/V AERANDIR, TWO PERSONS ON BOARD,
   WITHIN THREE MILES OF 45-56.79N 017-05.14W
   AT 140651Z JUL. VESSELS IN VICINITY
   REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST
   IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC FALMOUTH.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1329/10.
